'''''Masters of the Universe: The Arcade Game''''' is a [[platform game]] developed by [[Adventure Soft]] for the [[Amstrad CPC]], [[BBC Micro]], [[Commodore 64]], and [[ZX Spectrum]] and published by [[U.S. Gold]] in 1987. The game is part of the [[Masters of the Universe]] [[media franchise]].  The Commodore 64 version is titled '''''He-Man and the Masters of the Universe: The Ilearth Stone'''''.<ref>{{lemon64 game|id=1180|name=
He-Man and the Masters of the Universe: The Ilearth Stone}}</ref>

In the same year, U.S. Gold also published ''[[Masters of the Universe: The Super Adventure]]''.

